# Final Report

Use this protocol node to prepare the final report after QC passes.

## Inputs

Final summary: {{var|final_summary: AiralogyMarkdown, title = "Final summary"}}

QC passed: {{var|qc_pass: bool = false, title = "QC passed"}}

Reviewer: {{var|reviewer: UserName, title = "Reviewer"}}

## Review

{{step|draft_report, check=True}} Draft the report from the prepared sample, measurement output, and QC analysis.

{{check|report_ready}} Confirm that the report is ready for release.
